---
import Title from "@/components/Titles.astro";
---

<section
  class="w-full flex flex-col justify-between items-center mx-auto mt-20 mb-36"
>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col justify-around items-center max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-[10%] lg:px-10 relative"
  >
    <Title
      title="Discover "
      titleBlue="Our Story"
      subtitle="get to know"
      desc="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vestibulum convallis."
      layout="right"
    />
  </div>

  <div
    class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-[10%] lg:px-10 gap-4 mt-20"
  >
    <img
      src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/image/story.webp`}
      alt=""
      class="w-full h-96 max-w-md object-cover"
    />
    <div
      class="w-full flex flex-col justify-start items-start gap-4 max-w-md font-archivo text-base md:text-lg font-light text-secondary-700 dark:text-secondary-300 text-pretty"
    >
      <p>
        Founded in 2012, our agency was born out of a shared love for design,
        technology, and the limitless possibilities of the web.
      </p>
      <p>
        We started as a small group of individuals who believed in the power of
        the internet to shape businesses and create meaningful online
        experiences.
      </p>
      <p>
        From our humble beginnings in a cozy office space, we've grown into a
        dynamic and highly skilled team of experts, united by the common goal of
        making the web a better place, one pixel at a time.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our dedication to quality, innovation, and collaboration has been the
        driving force behind our success.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
